headline: Did Strong Q3 Results and a Dividend Hike Just Shift Regency Centers' (REG) Investment Narrative?
summary: Regency Centers Corporation recently announced its third quarter 2025 results, reporting year-over-year increases in revenue, net income, and Same Property Net Operating Income, alongside a raised full-year earnings guidance and a more than 7% dividend increase on its common stock.
